snippet.textDisplay:
So Chris was in the cage the whole time behind a curved mirror. The footage of him in the Trex was shot before the jump. There was a cut right before the Trex started its run, that is where the other driver was switched in. The ramp had another ramp trap door that the Trex went into and Chris came out from behind the mirror when the camera was blinded by the real/fake flames. I say real/fake because they had flame cannons and I'm sure some of the flame were real. However at editing I bet you could still see Chris getting out from behind the mirror so they added the obviously fake flames. Really..really bad.
I think Chris did this so he could right off the Trex as a business expense.
